dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibex4lin.lincommunication

Interface ILinScheduleTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface ILinScheduleTable
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    ILinScheduleTable: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    The master task (in the master node) transmits frame headers based on a schedule table. The schedule table specifies the identifiers for each header and the interval between the start of a frame and the start of the following frame.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!

      • getPriority

        long getPriority()
        Query the value of the attribute Priority.

        Priority of the schedule table. The priority is used in the schedule table manager. The RUN_ONCE run mode schedules shall not have equal priority. Priority 0 is reserved for the NULL_SCHEDULE. Priority 255 is reserved for the RUN_CONTINUOUS run mode.

        Returns:
        The value or null
